snippet.title: Definitely Not Experts
snippet.description: Whether its sports talk or random conversation. Definitely Not Experts will be able to provide you with hours of entertainment. Between The Sports Show and The Other Show youll get the perfect mental break you need to recharge and tackle the rest of your day. Or relax and have a good laugh. Heston and Damien are building an inclusive culture and community of supportive like minded people that are looking to have fun, but get to work too. Just remember to not take anything they say too seriously because they are Definitely Not Experts.
